name: SAINIK LAMINATED DOORS
Prod_desc: Sainik Laminated Doors are borer and termite resistant doors that offer the perfect combination of style and substance, that fits your budget perfectly. These doors are covered with High Pressure Laminates, giving them the beautiful finish that complements the strength of SAINIK. They are easy to clean and maintain.
Prod_usps: Boiling Water Proof , Climate Stable , Borer & Termite Resistant , Superior Surface Finish
